        "E1": "## Recommendation: Option D (Retroactive resentencing) paired with Option A's framework going forward\n\nThe binding constraint here is not drug policy philosophy. It is prison population and the $1.8B corrections budget against a moderate governor's signature. Every other framing is downstream of that.",
